snippet.title: Cats vs Cthulhu Steam release trailer
snippet.description:
Cats vs Cthulhu is a casual survivor-like where you play as a cat the Destroyer of the Great Old Ones. Arm yourself with yarns, fruits and other delicacies. Dress up in the most stylish outfit possible. Find a way to become the ultimate weapon.

Wishlist game on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3270620/Cats_vs_Cthulhu/
Play game in your browser here: https://jokerddzz.itch.io/cats-vs-cthulhu

If you have any suggestions you can find me here: https://discord.gg/JfuwjGwNeU

Have a good one. 

#indiegame #roguelike #rougelite #bullethell #bulletheaven #cozy #cute #sweet #cat #cats #candy #colorful
